channel.title: Report on Mechanical Weathering
channel.description: So... two problems. One, I have a two-page essay on mechanical weathering due tomorrow. This brings me to the second problem: I'm lazy and busy with a few class finals anyway. I request that the self-declared intellectuals of moparisthebest do my homework for me. If you take on this small task, I'll perform a subtle miracle [i]just for you.[/i] If you take up the job, please tell me so I don't start on it after wearing out my poor mind on my finals.
